short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: The VINTEL extension will automatically capture VINs to view the diagnostic reports through the tools you're already familiar with.

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Introducing the new VINTEL browser extension.  Now you can easily access VinTel Diagnostic Status Reports from anywhere.  Use your existing systems and enable the VinTel extension to quickly access the specific DSR by VIN.  You can easily view, print, share, and download the VINTEL DSRs.
